Aninri bụ ọchịchị ime obodo na steeti Enugu, Naijiria
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị n'obodo Ndeabo
Ọchịchị ime obodo dị ihe dị ka mmadụ 233,723 dị ka ọnụ ọgụgụ ndị mmadụ tụrụ anya ya si na ngụkọ 2006 siri dị
Annri bụ obodo ise;  Oduma, Nenwe, Ndeabo, Mpu na Okpanku
Oduma bụ nke kacha n'ime mmadụ ise nwere ihe dị ka puku mmadụ iri itoolu na asatọ bi na 2006
Gọọmenti ime obodo ewepụtala ndị ama ama ma n'Enugwu steeti na Naịjirịa n'ozuzu ya, gụnyere onye bụbu onyeisi ụlọ ọgbakọ omebe iwu Enugu steeti Abel Chukwu, onye bụbu onyeisi oche steeti Enugu
nke People's Democratic Party Late Igwe Onyioha Nwanjoku (Ndumeze 1 of Ndumeze), osote onye isi oche nke Senate Nigeria Ike Ekweremmadu onye bụ DSP site na 2007 ruo 2015 na 2015-ruo taa
Annri nwere oke oke na Nkanu-East n'ebe ugwu ọwụwa anyanwụ yana Awgu n'ebe ugwu ọdịda anyanwụ
Emebere ọchịchị obodo site na Ochie Awgu LGA n'afọ 1996
Ọ ga-akpọ aha, Awgu South LGA ruo mgbe ndị isi ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị nke mpaghara ahụ họọrọ ịga site na njirimara dị iche na mpụga Awgu a ma ama
Mpaghara kansụl ime obodo na-etinyekarị aka n'ihe ọkụkụ.
Enwere ike ịnweta Aninri site na okporo ụzọ Enugu-Portharcourt nwere opekata mpe ụzọ anọ nwere okporo ụzọ mara mma
Site: Onwe junction, Nenwe junction, Mgbowo junction na Aki na Ukwa junction.
Aninri nwere mpaghara nke 364 km2 na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ 233,723 na ọnụ ọgụgụ afọ 2006.
Koodu ozi nke mpaghara ahụ bụ 402.
